    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust E46 M3 featuring the iconic S54B32 high-revving inline-six engine. This unit utilizes six individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing for exceptional throttle response. Power is delivered through a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M differential lock. Crucially, this example has received rear subframe reinforcement and a VANOS overhaul, addressing common chassis and timing vulnerabilities. The suspension retains its original geometry, providing a communicative and balanced handling profile. While displaying minor aesthetic patina, the drivetrain remains tight, the compression is consistent across all cylinders, and the cooling system has been refreshed to ensure thermal efficiency during spirited driving.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
