      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously maintained and serves as a prime example of its model year. Finished in a classic deep metallic paint that still retains a high-gloss luster, the exterior shows only the minor road wear expected of a well-loved driver. Inside, the leather upholstery remains supple and free of tears, complemented by a smoke-free cabin and a fully functional suite of electronics. Mechanically, it is robust; I have kept a comprehensive folder of all service records, including recent fluid changes and a fresh set of premium tires. It handles precisely and shifts smoothly, offering a confident and comfortable ride. While there are a few light stone chips on the front fascia, the overall presentation is excellent for anyone seeking a reliable, high-performing car that has been cared for by a detail-oriented owner.",
