      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that\u2019s reliable, super comfy, and ready for your next road trip? I\u2019ve absolutely loved driving this car, and it\u2019s been taken care of really well. It\u2019s got a few minor signs of life here and there, but it runs like a dream and is ready to find its next home. Come take it for a spin\u2014I promise you\u2019ll fall in love with how smooth it feels on the road!",
