      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333 hp with a visceral 8,000 RPM redline. The powertrain is mated to a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement, ensuring structural rigidity under high lateral loads. Equipped with the factory variable M differential lock and a finely tuned multi-link rear suspension, this chassis offers telepathic feedback and neutral handling balance. The exterior displays minor patina consistent with spirited use, while the interior remains driver-focused and functional. A mechanically sound example of BMW\u2019s finest naturally aspirated era, optimized for the driving purist.",
